kpi_info.title: BTS HSPA USER AMOUNT UTILIZATION IN UL - CLASS 3
kpi_info.use: The counter shows how many utilization rate samples have been detected within the (70 - <80)% class per uplink direction. Each utilization rate sample calculates the number of HSUPA users in use divided by the licenced number of HSUPA users. UPDATED: The counter is incremented when the sample of the utilization rate is within (70 - <80)% class.
